headline: NMTC Stock Gains as FDA Clears OneRF System for Facial Pain Treatment
summary: NeuroOne stock rallies after FDA clears its OneRF system, a minimally invasive solution targeting severe facial pain, scheduled to launch in late 2025.

headline: Cooper Companies' Innovation Fuels Growth Amid Macro Headwinds
summary: COO leans on innovation and diversification to fuel growth, but fertility softness, tariffs and inventory headwinds weigh on near-term outlook.

headline: Nilesh Shah joins Illumina as Head of Region, AMEA
summary: Illumina Inc. (NASDAQ: ILMN), a global leader in DNA sequencing and array-based technologies, announced today the appointment of Nilesh Shah as Head of Region, AMEA, effective immediately.
